  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tempeh and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the red pepper flakes, cumin, and paprika, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes and vegetable broth, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Season the stew with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
